message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as it deals with audio and speech processing. cs.SI is also likely as it deals with signal processing. cs.LG is another possibility as it deals with machine learning and neural networks. cs.MM is also possible as it deals with multimedia and music processing. cs.IR is less likely but still possible as it deals with information retrieval and could be relevant for downbeat tracking in music.
